original_title: Elaine Dart, Not Like Other People
overview: This documentary shows Elaine Dart's success in dealing with cerebral palsy. Through perseverance and patience, she learns to use her feet to accomplish such intricate tasks as threading a needle, stringing beads, and knitting.

production_companies.name: The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints
